      "id": 393348,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "Please note, since this report was submitted and resolved, Oberlo has been removed from scope for our program. **We are no longer accepting reports on Oberlo at the time of this disclosure.**\n\nOberlo was an application that integrated with the Shopify platform. It was designed to simplify the process of sourcing and importing products from various suppliers into a Shopify store.\n\nDue to missing access control checks on the backend, a user with limited permissions on an Oberlo account was able to modify the Oberlo subscription for the associated account.",
